 plasma-desktop (4:5.20.5-4+deb11u1.lnd.32) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   * Modified the bug where the user avatar does not update on the user details page.
   * Since the variable usersDetailPage.user.face is always set to user's name(eg:loongson),
   * it get an old picture from the cache. To resolve: add a timestamp to create a new URL
   * for fetch a new picture.
